<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Food on Luke Jaeger</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/tags/food/</link><description>Recent content in Food on Luke Jaeger</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://trickfilm.github.io/tags/food/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Pizzeria Somewhere In Boston's South End, ca 1985, Drawn From Memory</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/pizzeria-somewhere-in-boston-south-end-1985-drawn-from-memory/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/pizzeria-somewhere-in-boston-south-end-1985-drawn-from-memory/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A hazy and fragmented memory of a pizza place I stumbled into, probably in the company of &lt;a href="http://www.worlddreambank.org/2/2DRMSCEN.HTM"&gt;Dan Holzner&lt;/a&gt;, during one of our marijuana-fueled rambles around the Fenway and South End.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Still Life With Chickens &amp; Fruit</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/still-life-with-chickens--fruit/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/still-life-with-chickens--fruit/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Taco Stand, Mexico City</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/taco-stand-mexico-city/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/taco-stand-mexico-city/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Not the greatest scan, but I like the flavor.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Beef</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/beef/</link><pubDate>Fri, 30 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/beef/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The eternal delights of wet concrete.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How To Ask If The Convenience Store Sells Hard-Boiled Eggs When None Of The Staff Speak English Or Spanish</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/how-to-ask-if-the-convenience-store-sells-hard-boiled-eggs-when-none-of-the-staff-speak-english-or-spanish/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/how-to-ask-if-the-convenience-store-sells-hard-boiled-eggs-when-none-of-the-staff-speak-english-or-spanish/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Breakfast In Budapest</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/breakfast-in-budapest/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/breakfast-in-budapest/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Software and spraypaint! I laser cut CMYK halftones out of oilboard to make stencils, then &amp;ldquo;printed&amp;rdquo; them with spraypaint. It worked! I especially like the oranges.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Text Satan!</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/text-satan/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/text-satan/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Some co-workers and I stopped into this beaten-down Italian pastry shop in New Haven one evening. It was raining buckets and the place was about to close. The girl behind the counter kept yelling into her phone (it was a little hard to tell when she was talking to us and when she wasn&amp;rsquo;t) and the screen was smashed, so she could only use the phone by voice commands. She explained that she was trying to text her boyfriend, who was listed in her contacts as &amp;lsquo;Satan&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Rabbit Tracks (Picnic In The Graveyard)</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/picnic-in-the-graveyard/</link><pubDate>Fri, 25 May 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/picnic-in-the-graveyard/</guid><description>&lt;p&g